  <CalDefinition Description="This CAL is intended to enable/disable Pay Broadcast Traffic Service (TMC and TPEG). When this CAL is set to 1 (TRUE), this service is enabled or supported. When this CAL is set to 0 (FALSE), this service is disabled or not supported. [ Old MY20 NAV ]; THIS CALIBRATION SHOULD NOT BE USED FOR APPLICATIONS USING GAS" Name="PAY_BROADCAST_TRAFFIC" References="GIS-620 Navigation Functional Requirements" Usage="MID,HIGH,VCU,GLOBALA,GLOBALB">
    <CalID>_tu3JkMqLEeW_5NzJEimJmA</CalID>
